com.stripe.android.model

Class SetupIntent.Error

  • com.stripe.android.model.SetupIntent.Error
  • Enclosing class:
    SetupIntent

    public static class SetupIntent.Error

    The error encountered in the previous SetupIntent confirmation. See last_setup_error.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      java.lang.String code
      For some errors that could be handled programmatically, a short string indicating the error code reported.
      java.lang.String declineCode
      For card errors resulting from a card issuer decline, a short string indicating the card issuer’s reason for the decline if they provide one.
      java.lang.String docUrl
      A URL to more information about the error code reported.
      java.lang.String message
      A human-readable message providing more details about the error. For card errors, these messages can be shown to your users.
      java.lang.String param
      If the error is parameter-specific, the parameter related to the error. For example, you can use this to display a message near the correct form field.
      PaymentMethod paymentMethod
      The PaymentMethod object for errors returned on a request involving a PaymentMethod.
      Error.Type type
      The type of error returned.
